Component Description
React Frontend: Single-page application built with React, providing a responsive and interactive user interface optimized for quick data entry.
API Gateway: Central entry point for all client requests. Handles routing and request validation.
Product Service: Manages all CRUD operations for products and inventory levels. Handles low-stock alerts.
Sales Service: Manages the creation of sales, updates inventory levels, and calculates totals and taxes.
Supplier Service: Manages supplier information and links them to products.
Report Service: Generates various business reports by aggregating data from sales and products.
Database: Persistent storage for user data, products, sales transactions, and supplier information.
Clerk: Third-party authentication service handling user registration and login.

